> > >>finished
> > >> with his, and then gave Mel a huge hug for what also probably
> > >>seemed
> > >> like an eternity.
> > >> As a note to those of you who might not be familiar with
> > >>military
> > >> protocol, the subordinate normally initiates a salute and will
